    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Having a function that configure SearchParameter on the <InstantSearch/> component feel more natural to me than having several <Configure/> widget. But if it's really easier for changing refinements dynamically that's a real advantage. \n\nIn either case that's great, I will need this feature in a near future :) \n",
